                  <summary>One of the 70 Mughal documents including farmāns, ḥukmnāmah, iqrārnāmah, chaknāmah etc. relating to the family of<persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied">Jalāl al-Dīn,<foreign xml:lang="fa">جلال الدین</foreign>
